    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a requirement to activate this jutsu, you must currently be in the <em><strong>Death Fist Stance</strong></em>.</p><p>You manifest a light blue snowflake-shaped compass underneath yourself, as chakra begins to seep into the air from it and derive information from the surroundings. The compass needle points then light up in accordance with your opponent's strength, the stronger they are the more that light up. Finally, after gauging their strength your technique focuses your body to sense their battle spirit, allowing you to target their vitals easier and adapt to their fighting style.</p><p>While you are under the effects of this jutsu you gain the following;</p><ul><li>Once per turn you may reroll a melee attack roll.</li><li>For the duration, whenever you hit with a melee attack you increase your melee attack rolls by +1 when hitting that same target, until the start of your next turn.</li><li>You gain blindsight in a 60-foot sphere originating from you.</li><li>As a reaction to being targeted by a melee attack you can subtract their melee attack rolls by an amount equal to half your proficiency bonus, until the beginning of your next turn.</li><li>For the duration, your melee attack rolls cannot suffer any penalties.</li></ul>",
